short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension gives a minimalistic, full featured tab list

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sinax TabList is a minimalistic tab list extensions for Chrome. 
If you always have lots of tabs open and have trouble finding that specific tab, Sinax TabList is just for you!
